  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BioModule, JavaModule, ScriptModule, Comparable<BioModule>

    public class RemoveLowPathwayCounts
extends Humann2CountModule
implements JavaModule
    This BioModule set low Pathway counts below a configured threshold to zero.
    These low sample counts are assumed to be miscategorized or genomic contamination.
    GUI Module Name
    Remove Low Pathway Counts
